<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>{{subject}}</title>
<style>
  body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f8fafc; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif; color: #0f172a; }
  .wrap { max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; overflow: hidden; }
  .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d9488, #059669); padding: 28px 32px; }
  .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .header p { margin: 4px 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }
  .body { padding: 32px; }
  .body p { margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #334155; }
  .body p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .btn { display: inline-block; margin: 8px 0 20px; padding: 12px 24px; background: #0d9488; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; }
  .note { background: #f1f5f9; border-left: 3px solid #0d9488; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px 16px; margin: 16px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #475569; }
  .footer { border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 20px 32px; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; text-align: center; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <div class="header">
    <h1>{{organizationName}}</h1>
    <p>Tenant &amp; Property Management</p>
  </div>
  <div class="body">
    {{{body}}}
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>This email was sent by {{organizationName}} via the Landlord Management platform.</p>
    <p>If you did not expect this email, you can safely ignore it.</p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
